Visual Data Dictionary


An industrys market penetration rate tells us how many people have purchased a product or service relative to the market size. For Medicare Part D plans calculation for Penetration Rate is:

Penetration Rate = (Enrolled Population / Eligible Population) x 100

Tracking Penetration Rate is important for an industry in order to know how many new customers they are winning over.
